        </item>
        <item>
            <title>平治全新智能純電 EQA 及 EQB 到港，精緻設計風格、全新設計元素馬上睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=benz-eqa-eqb</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 13:05:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EQA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EQB]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平治]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256982</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新平治輕巧純電動車 EQA 及 EQB 近日正式到港。這兩個最新智能純電 SUV 從設計上就展現出一貫的精緻風格，並融入了多項全新設計元素。以下記者就帶大家到香港會場睇睇。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256983" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1441.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1442.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1398.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>平治純電動車 EQA 及 EQB 車頭的黑色板面鬼面罩配以平治星徽標誌，以及鍍鉻的星徽設計，提升了整體的辨識度。日間行車燈與燈帶相連，令車輛在夜間的視覺效果更為突出。全新 EQA 及 EQB 更加強了車頭的寬闊感覺，側面設計以高光黑色裝飾點綴霧燈位置，使車身更具現代感。此外，EQA 車型配備 AMG Line 套件，車身同色的輪拱飾邊和重新設計的尾燈進一步增強了車輛的運動風格。新推出的兩種車身顏色 &#8211; spectral blue 和 high-tech silver，使得車型選擇更加豐富。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1430.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>進入車內，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 提供了多項現代化的內籠設計，令駕駛者與乘客享有舒適且智能的乘坐體驗。配備觸控按鈕的最新一代方向盤，搭配平治星徽標誌及平治圖案背光飾板，增添了豪華感。內飾板採用了激光雕刻技術，並具備發光功能，為車廂增添了一抹亮點。標準配備的 10.25 吋中央顯示屏，與車內其他高級車款的風格一致，進一步強調了平治電動車的高品質。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1457.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1455.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1461.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256991" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1471.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在中控台部分，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 均配備了最新的 MBUX 多媒體系統，該系統擁有零層級觸控介面，令駕駛者無需滾動介面或使用語音控制即可操作相關功能。此外，車內還配備了選配的 Burmester 環迴音響系統，並支援 Dolby Atmos 全景聲效，提供身臨其境的聽覺體驗。駕駛者可根據個人喜好，從三種風格（簡約、運動、經典）及三種模式（導航、駕駛輔助、服務）中進行選擇，並能設置 10 種不同的車廂氣氛燈顏色，創造專屬的個性化空間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256992" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1468.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1467.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1470.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在科技系統方面，全新的 EQA 及 EQB 提供了多達四種 Sound Experiences，這些聲效可透過中央顯示屏選擇或關閉，為駕駛者及乘客帶來不同的聽覺體驗。當駕駛者靠近並進入車廂時，車輛會發出迎接的聲效，離開時亦會伴隨特定的 Aura 聲效。行駛時的聲效能夠隨著油門踏板位置、車速等變化，帶來更具互動性的駕駛體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1484.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1465.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1448.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在安全性方面，EQA 和 EQB 均配備了升級的駕駛輔助系統和感應技術。全新的 mono-multipurpose 攝像機和倒車攝像機能夠提供更準確的視野，而主動式車道保持輔助系統則能提供更舒適的轉向幹預。此外，車輛還配備了 360°泊車鏡頭，駕駛者可以更直觀快捷地完成泊車操作，無論是在平行停車位還是垂直停車位中，都能輕鬆泊車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1453.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1450.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1446.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>最後，行車安全方面，全新 EQA 和 EQB 均具備先進的熱管理系統，並標準配備熱泵。這不僅提升了車內的舒適性，還大幅降低了電池電量的消耗，進而延長了車輛的續航距離。EQA 車型的續航距離最高可達 569 公里（根據 WLTP 標準），而 EQB 則提供類似的性能表現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1257001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026-694x443.png" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026-694x443.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024081890026.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/13/benz-level-4-auto-drive-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">平治獲批北京 Lv4 自動駕駛測試　測試車設冗餘系統 + 無需人類隨時接管</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/09/mercedes-benz-eqs-facelift-spy-photos/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Facelift 版 2025 年推出，平治 EQS 新車諜照曝光</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/08/mercedes-benz-seized-over-1-6-mil-counterfeit-parts-in-2023/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">平治截獲逾 160 萬件偽冒零件，全球各地突擊檢查 740 次</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/benz-eqa-eqb/life-tech/auto/">平治全新智能純電 EQA 及 EQB 到港，精緻設計風格、全新設計元素馬上睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
